embarrassing tirade: ``There are a certain few media people out
there who won't get the opportunity to talk to myself and the rest
of the guys. We know who you are. We know who you scumbags are who
are trashing us and treating us like garbage.'' ... Among the
venues where the Patriots and Oilers have played through the years:
Nickerson Field, Jeppesen Stadium (Houston), Fenway Park, Rice
Stadium, Boston College's Alumni Stadium, the Astrodome, and
Schaefer/Sullivan/Foxboro Stadium.
</P>
