<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-20 17:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4916 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ONLINE-PRIVACY-ART-2T     09-20 1071
