<SLUG> BC-LADN-SPORTS-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Sept. 21 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Brad Nelson at (818) 713-3602.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-ANGELS-MARINERS (Anaheim, Calif.) _ The Anaheim Angels face
the Seattle Mariners at 5 p.m. PDT.
</P>
<P>
   By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BBA-ANGELNOTES (Anaheim, Calif.) _ Notebook from the
Angels-Mariners game.
</P>
<P>
   By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-USC (Los Angeles) _ Analysis of USC's win over Oregon State.
</P>
<P>
   By Scott Wolf. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-UCLA (Houston) _ Analysis of UCLA's win over Houston.
</P>
<P>
   By Jon Wilner. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BBN-DODGERS (San Francisco) _ The Dodgers face the Giants.
</P>
<P>
   By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BBN-DODGERS-NOTES (San Francisco) _ Dodgers notebook.
</P>
<P>
   By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BOX-ROSENTHAL-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Weekly boxing column.
</P>
<P>
   By Michael Rosenthal. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   GEN-HOFFARTH-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Weekly notes column.
</P>
<P>
   By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
