<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-GERMANY-POLITICS-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   GERMANY-POLITICS (Hanover) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Sept. 20.
</P>
</TEXT>
