   MOVIES-BOX-OFFICE (Los Angeles) _ Action-comedy ``Rush Hour''
zipped past rivals on its way to a record-setting fall-season
opening with an estimated $31 million at 2,658 theaters nationwide
during the Friday-Sunday period, studios sources said. By Dave
McNary. (Will move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California news
