   CSUN-ALUMS (Los Angeles) _ One is an immigrant from China who
became one of the nation's leading role models in education reform.
Another started flying a plane as a boy and pursued a career that
would take him higher _ to the stars. These are just some of CSUN's
top alums. By Sharline Chiang. (Will move in the ``n'' California
