   INSIDE STORIES PROMOTED ON PAGE 1:
</P>
<P>
   HURRICANE-GEORGES (San Juan, P.R.) _ Hurricane Georges bears
down on the Caribbean. It is expected to hit the Leeward Islands
Sunday night. By Larry Rohter.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9:20 p.m. ET in ``a'' news file.)
</P>
