<SLUG> BC-TV-TALK-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Biggest new show this season? Maybe the presidential testimony
 &HT;    (EDS: Moving in (w) Washington and (E) Entertainment
categories.)
